{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "bmk-collection-v2",
		"name": "BusyMumKitchen API v2",
		"description": "Complete API collection for BusyMumKitchen — KFC-style food ordering backend.\n\nBase path: `/api/v1`\n\n## Auth Flow\n1. **Send OTP** → OTP printed in server console (dev mode)\n2. **Verify OTP** → tokens auto-saved to environment\n3. All authenticated endpoints use Bearer token automatically\n\n## Roles\n- `CUSTOMER` — orders, cart, profile\n- `ADMIN` — categories, menu, orders, coupons, analytics, customers\n- `KITCHEN_STAFF` — kitchen dashboard, queue, accept/prepare/ready\n- `DELIVERY_PARTNER` — assigned orders, delivery status\n\n## Order Flow (KFC-style)\n`PLACED → ACCEPTED → PREPARING → READY_FOR_PICKUP → OUT_FOR_DELIVERY → DELIVERED`\n\nDaily order numbers reset each day: `#001`, `#002`, `#003`...",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"auth": {
		"type": "bearer",
		"bearer": [
			{
				"key": "token",
				"value": "{{accessToken}}",
				"type": "string"
			}
		]
	},
	"variable": [],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "OTP-based mobile authentication with role-based access.\n\n**Dev Mode:** OTP is printed in server console logs.\n\nFlow: Send OTP → Verify OTP → Get JWT tokens → Use authenticated endpoints.",
